Available Tools: send_email | compose_draft | send_reply | forward_email
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": ["string"], "cc": ["string"], "subject": "string", "body": "string", "attachments": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "status": "sent|draft|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Email the safety inspection results to the facility manager.
Call: { "func_call": "send_email", "to": ["facility.mgr@buildco.com"], "cc": ["safety@buildco.com"], "subject": "Safety Inspection Report - Building B", "body": "Hi,\n\nAttached are the results from today's safety inspection in Building B. No critical issues were found, but two minor repairs are recommended.\n\nRegards,\nInspector J. Smith", "attachments": ["inspection_report_b_nov01.pdf"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_10293m", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T09:20:15Z" }

